title: Dominant Transport Services
description: In 2023, transport services accounted for 87.07% of Djibouti's service imports, highlighting its strategic role in regional logistics.

title: High Youth Unemployment
description: In 2024, Djibouti had a youth unemployment rate of 76.32% for ages 15-24, indicating significant challenges in youth employment.

title: Booming Export Growth
description: Djibouti's export value index reached 2455.37 in 2021, showing a substantial increase since 2015.

title: Minimal Government Spending on Secondary Education
description: In 2016, Djibouti's government expenditure per secondary student was only 0.73% of GDP per capita, one of the lowest globally.
